{"tid":106593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【走資fail】滬旅客帶千萬日圓出境　遭海關發現充公","createTime":"2017-02-03T18:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T05:55:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb203ad33d6ef5f10275ed1f4a37f9f4de5a2bd9","tid":106593,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486106789_d407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486106789_d407.jpg&h=ef536fac&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上海浦東國際機場海關日前截查一名出境中國旅客，在他的隨身行李中發現疊裝整齊的1,060萬日圓（約72.5萬港元）現金。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，這名中國旅客通過無申報通道，在接受海關檢查時，其行李的X光圖像有可疑。經過覆查，海關關員判斷這名旅客存在違規攜帶貨幣的嫌疑。開箱查驗後，海關關員發現疊裝整齊的1,060萬日幣現金。<br />\n<br />\n根據國家對貨幣出入境的管理規定，旅客進出境每人每次攜帶的人民幣現鈔限額為2萬元。若確需攜帶超過折合美元5,000元的外幣現鈔出境，應向銀行及外匯管理局申領《攜帶外匯出境許可證》，出境時海關憑證驗放。涉事旅客並無法提供相關許可證明，案件已移交海關緝私部門作進一步處理。"},{"pid":"becd31c6a75b9b9dc7e246d7286221b3c29e427f","tid":106593,"uid":9571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:34:29.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"13f1b683e880d11d9c724760dc405599cf7cf52c","tid":106593,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:40:10.000Z","msg":"幅圖係美金嚟喎老細<br />\n<br />\n去一次日本豪洗一千萬yen, 對大陸土豪嚟講應該濕濕碎啫"},{"pid":"c344761cf8a860e6d105b99403f9e2d29ff989d6","tid":106593,"uid":41928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T20:24:25.000Z","msg":"富蘭克林幾時入籍日本尬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db99ed3266307d64de3a1c66624567ec7d02b7ae","tid":106593,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T01:39:19.000Z","msg":"日圓幾時出100蚊紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd60cb424a5961fd8a56e3a013f490cd80492293","tid":106593,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新日元"},{"pid":"d7d450cb73a8238f167567b0848684e481ed407d","tid":106593,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新日元</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d473964f43f6999104b409fec008d440a18016","tid":106593,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f568f66569e328848faf63827eef5e4566acdcf","tid":106593,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:20:35.000Z","msg":"美式日元？"},{"pid":"040d56b1941015bc5a3d700c0200cb547a0d0bbc","tid":106593,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:12:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日圓</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50261ac8f643f76c7767b6925446e8d7638e0fdd","tid":106593,"uid":45650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"若確需攜帶超過折合美元5,000元的外幣現鈔出境，應向銀行及外匯管理局申領《攜帶外匯出境許可證》<br />\n<br />\n一定係D海關為左方便計數，所以即場將D日元兌晒做美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9ab1b99b55fa8974c56f7887af4246a6146273","tid":106593,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:49:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c956b31dfe2ec1b3e4f26df920c5c981e285a8f","tid":106593,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"查檢千萬美金，經處理後發還千萬日